This is the back-end Time Server. Every second a piece of data is generated and exposed through the endpoint
/streamTime, for SSE events use /streamTime/sse

This application requires flask module and flask_cors
($ pip install flask, flask_cors)

To run it on local environment use the following commands:

$ export FLASK_APP=webSetviceStream.py
$ flask run

This will run on the default port 5000.